84121, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 要说贸易壁垒，美国一辆日系车或者德系车售价多少，中国一辆日系车或者德系车售价多少？", "timestamp": 1657084121}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277363, "create_time": 1657084275, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Alice: 这不叫动态清零？\n![](https://bafkreibohvwe4qdn76s6b44zoxngp4hstdah76pwpyb6tw2vxljfunfws4.ipfs.dweb.link/?filename=v2-66c48d7add6268fae5bd65d2cfa70e12_720w%20(1).jpg&filetype=image%2Fjpeg) [加载失败请点击此](https://t-hole.red/ipfs.html#bafkreibohvwe4qdn76s6b44zoxngp4hstdah76pwpyb6tw2vxljfunfws4)\n\n---\n", "timestamp": 1657084275}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277366, "create_time": 1657084338, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Grace: 6月确实不错，不过只恢复到了2月的水平，和疫情前还差得远呢。而且6月的好景象我认为只是暂时的，上一波疫情刚结束，下一波疫情还没来", "timestamp": 1657084338}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277380, "create_time": 1657084620, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Francis: 这都行的话那官媒做的实在是太棒了", "timestamp": 1657084620}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277387, "create_time": 1657084789, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 对外投资，一带一路，稳定汇率，技术引进。", "timestamp": 1657084789}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277394, "create_time": 1657084925, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 你自己去下个中国的国际收支表，看看问题出在什么地方。巨额的错误与遗漏账户数值是怎么回事？", "timestamp": 1657084925}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277400, "create_time": 1657085219, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Eve: 疫情前是2019年吗？敢情2020、2021两年都是负增长？你的认知和现实脱节的有点大。", "timestamp": 1657085219}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277403, "create_time": 1657085326, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Grace: 那你怎么不去喷“6月是2月以来最好的一个月”这个说法？3月4月5月也没有负增长啊？", "timestamp": 1657085326}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277406, "create_time": 1657085366, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Grace: 现在人们对中国经济增长的预期显然比2019年时差得多", "timestamp": 1657085366}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277410, "create_time": 1657085453, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 你这问得就满满的民科风了...", "timestamp": 1657085453}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277414, "create_time": 1657085521, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 你认为国际金融的术语民科？", "timestamp": 1657085521}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277416, "create_time": 1657085553, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 人家这是给懂行的人看的，“巨额的错误与遗漏账户数值”，真要是这样为啥没有新闻热点？", "timestamp": 1657085553}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277439, "create_time": 1657085815, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 央行拿自己的信誉开玩笑？", "timestamp": 1657085815}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277440, "create_time": 1657085925, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 中国巨额资金非法外逃又不是啥秘密\nhttp://finance.sina.com.cn/zl/china/2017-09-27/zl-ifymesii5978281.shtml", "timestamp": 1657085925}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277441, "create_time": 1657085976, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 只不过官媒天天吹顺差，大部分人如果不关注相关数据，也不会注意到问题", "timestamp": 1657085976}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277444, "create_time": 1657086006, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Francis: 测算资金非法外逃的研究一大堆", "timestamp": 1657086006}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277452, "create_time": 1657086142, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Eve: 外储是拿来用的，不然就是一堆绿纸随着人家放水而贬值。外汇储备减去外债这个算法就很搞笑，外债又不是用当前的外汇储备偿还的，很多国家的外债都远比外汇储备要高，更别说美国这样的外债动不动比GDP还要高的国家。", "timestamp": 1657086142}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277458, "create_time": 1657086395, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Grace: 对大部分国家来说，外汇储备够还外债的利息就够可以了。对美国来说印钱还债就可以了。通胀之类的副作用另说。", "timestamp": 1657086395}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277465, "create_time": 1657086583, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "兑不到外币的韭菜们看着顺差以为形势一片大好，真正赚到了外汇的却在偷偷搬家。对外投资？且不说写在国际收支表的对外投资根本弥补不了差额，所谓的对外投资真正到用的时候会不会发现进了私人口袋根本没法用呢", "timestamp": 1657086583}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277470, "create_time": 1657086789, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 美元都放水成啥样子了，还以为换到美元就是赚到啊。", "timestamp": 1657086789}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277483, "create_time": 1657087088, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "Re Francis: 给你几个数据更新一下自己对世界形势的认识：根据商务部网站14日消息，2022年1-5月，全国实际使用外资金额5642亿元人民币，同比增长17.3%，折合877.7亿美元，同比增长22.6%。\n\n从来源地看，韩国、美国、德国实际对华投资分别增长52.8%、27.1%、21.4%。\n\n这还是在美联储加息的大背景下。", "timestamp": 1657087088}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 277485, "create_time": 1657087143, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Grace: 你用人民币买国外大宗商品么？中俄交易都大部分